high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Pick up the champagne glass under the salt near the wall to the left.
Turn right and take two steps then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the champagne glass in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a step then turn right to face the table.
Put the glass on the table under the spatula.
